{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"43836-chunu-munu-let-us-play-now","title":"Chunu & Munu: Let Us Play Now","description":"A delightful little poem about finding different friends and games to play.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Brian Kavanagh"],"illustrators":["Abin  Shrestha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/43836-chunu-munu-let-us-play-now"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101411/size3/4dd94196a38d62e7e32b5d1c61647bfc.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101411/size6/4dd94196a38d62e7e32b5d1c61647bfc.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79793/size6/481ddfc8a1dcf43becf313e8e0f01ae6.jpg","text":"Who do we play with?\nLet’s play with friends.\nWhat shall we play with?\nLet’s play with stones.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79794/size6/28f0d31862c639139afa637d5d87e94a.jpg","text":"Who do we play with?\nLet’s play with friends.\nWhat shall we play?\nLet’s play on the swing.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79795/size6/434792e6a3777b7070d64154971fcfb3.jpg","text":"Who do we play with?\nLet’s play with our younger sister.\nWhat shall we play?\nLet’s skip with our rope.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79797/size6/19dbe975fb52a1e8dca3a860ec1a00d2.jpg","text":"Who do we play with?\nLet’s play with our brother.\nWhat shall we play?\nLet’s play on the slide.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79798/size6/9ea6aa59d912312fa2cc80e099e45b9b.jpg","text":"Who do we play with?\nLet’s play with our older sister.\nWhat shall we play?\nLet’s ask riddles.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79799/size6/3d6023822bcaad4b3eef424853c12fc1.jpg","text":"Who do we play with?\nLet’s play with our cousins.\nWhat shall we play?\nLet’s play hide-and-seek.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79800/size6/97624776d007aaa8aefe84b6489e11ec.jpg","text":"Who do we play with?\nFind a friend.\nAnd if you are alone?\nKick the Chungi ball* with your feet.\n*A ball made with rubber bands.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":136}}